headline: Ranpak Holdings: No Change In Sentiment As 2024 Nears Its End
summary: Ranpak's revenue rose to $92.2 million in Q3, driven by a 28.4% increase in Void-Fill machine sales. Read why I maintain my hold rating for PACK stock.
